content: My 6 month old loves the app, but she exits it by accident constantly. The app allows the notification drawer, menu long press, home, and back button actions that all exit the app. It would be better if only home or back was allowed and required you to confirm exit.
Only wish it had an app lock.

Thank you for writing this fantastic app, and for making it ad free too. It was well worth the money to buy it. I do recommend you have it use the full screen to avoid accidental pressing on the navbar and status bar.
